156
0:09:29.410 --> 0:09:33.267
1 o 2 (pocos)

157
0:09:34.000 --> 0:09:36.000
Chacal.

158
0:09:36.000 --> 0:09:38.000
Chacal? Ah

159
0:09:39.545 --> 0:09:43.324
Cerdos

160
0:09:43.817 --> 0:09:48.695
Huesos, pocos: 1 o 2

161
0:09:49.582 --> 0:09:55.643
